01:16:51.023 --> 01:16:52.224
Doesn't have to travel in time.

01:16:52.944 --> 01:16:54.243
Doesn't have to upend time.

01:16:54.284 --> 01:16:55.984
Doesn't have to rip the fabric of time.

01:16:57.905 --> 01:16:59.105
Ordinary progression.

01:17:00.506 --> 01:17:01.386
