01:17:17.073 --> 01:17:18.972
previously regarding Chanowk,

01:17:19.033 --> 01:17:20.853
but it's appropriate now.

01:17:21.592 --> 01:17:23.394
Chanowk, trained and prepared,

01:17:23.993 --> 01:17:25.234
dedicated and deployed,

01:17:26.094 --> 01:17:28.854
was unfazed by external human influences

01:17:28.935 --> 01:17:31.435
