01:17:32.095 --> 01:17:34.275
He, free of human cultural, societal,

01:17:34.336 --> 01:17:34.756
religious,

01:17:34.815 --> 01:17:36.356
or political control mechanisms,

01:17:36.856 --> 01:17:38.296
