01:17:45.500 --> 01:17:46.720
a man sent as a stem,

01:17:47.822 --> 01:17:49.842
the individual dispatched as a shoot,

01:17:50.542 --> 01:17:54.904
from Math - man, Shalach - sent out as,

01:17:55.225 --> 01:17:58.606
and a Shelach, a shoot, a stem,

01:17:59.648 --> 01:18:01.708
a sprout, a Choter.

01:18:03.277 --> 01:18:04.257
at three hundred years,

01:18:04.337 --> 01:18:06.078
and then he fathered other sons and

01:18:06.118 --> 01:18:06.519
